Package: Linear3
Type: Package
Title: Linear regression, ANOVA, hat matrix and Outlier Influence in Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiwen Feng
Maintainer: Xiwen Feng <xiwenf@umich.edu> 
Description: Mimic existing R functions for linear regression and ANOVA. Compute leverage values and three commonly used resisuals (standardized, internally studentized, and externally studentized residuals), as well as diagnostic statistics for identifying outliers (DFFITS, Cook's Distance).
